 (N = 74 marked fruits). Piper hispidum plants produced zero to 12 ripe infructescences per plant each night during peak production. Few ripe infructescences of P. hispidum were available during the dry season; however, ripe infructescences of C. sciadophylla, remained abundant.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Bonaccorso, Frank J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Winkelmann, John R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Shin, Danny", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Agrawal, Caroline I.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Aslami, Nadia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bonney, Caitlin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hsu, Andrea", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jekielek, Phoebe E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Knox, Allison K.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kopach, Stephen J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jennings, Tara D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lasky, Jesse R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Menesale, Sarah A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Richards, Jeannine H.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Rutland, Jessica A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sessa, Anna K.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Zhaurova, Luba", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kunz, Thomas H.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/ffbd7e633555ffa26dfa3cf2250e5c3e", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/1ba1e7bc79ab36026ff721b29c9fee72c9474e08145ce11ab7e2985a7c384a6a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/XBJGRW72", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/XBJGRW72", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/ac66d6987f391c9bf09f3f97be401ed6!/b253660-256226", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifi